"The Razorpay POS refund request has encountered an unexpected error code."
msgstr "ຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍຄືນເງິນຂອງ Razorpay POS ພົບກັບລະຫັດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດທີ່ບໍ່ຄາດຄິດ."

#. module: pos_razorpay
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/pos_razorpay/models/pos_payment_method.py:0
